\c 22
\s VaRubheni nevaGadhi nehafu yerudzi rwaManase vanoenda kunyika yavo
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Joshua wakadana VaRubheni neVaGadhi nehafu yerudzi rwaManase,
\v 2 ndokuti kwavari: Imwi makachengeta zvese Mozisi muranda waJehovha zvaakakurairai, nekuteerera kuinzwi rangu pane zvese zvandakakurairai.
\v 3 Hamuna kusiya hama dzenyu mazuva awa mazhinji kusvika nhasi, asi makachengeta faniro yemurairo waJehovha Mwari wenyu.
\v 4 Zvino ikozvino Jehovha Mwari wenyu wapa hama yenyu zororo, sezvaakataura kwavari; naizvozvo ikozvino dzokai imwi muende kumatende enyu kunyika yenhaka yenyu Mozisi muranda waJehovha yaakakupai mhiri kwaJoridhani.
\v 5 Asi chenjerai kwazvo kuita murairo nemutemo Mozisi muranda waJehovha waakakurairai, kuda Jehovha Mwari wenyu, nekufamba munzira dzake dzese, nekuchengeta mirairo yake, nekunamatira paari, nekumushumira nemoyo yenyu yese uye nemweya yenyu yese.
\v 6 Zvino Joshua wakavaropafadza ndokuvaendesa; zvino vakaenda kumatende avo.
\v 7 Zvino kuhafu yerudzi rwaManase Mozisi wakange apa \add nzvimbo\add* yeBhashani; asi kune imwe hafu yayo Joshuwa wakapa \add nzvimbo\add* pamwe nehama dzavo mhiri kwaJoridhani kumavirazuva. Zvino Joshua akavaendisa kuenda kumatende avo, akavaropafadza.
\v 8 Zvino wakataura kwavari achiti: Dzokerai nefuma zhinji kumatende enyu uye nemombe zhinji kwazvo nesirivha uye negoridhe uye nendarira uye nematare uye nenguvo zhinji, govanai zvakapambwa zvevavengi venyu nehama dzenyu.
\p
\v 9 Zvino vana vaRubheni nevana vaGadhi nehafu yerudzi rwaManase vakadzoka, ndokubva pavana vaIsraeri vakabuda paShiro munyika yeKenani kuenda kunyika yeGiriyadhi, kunyika yenhaka yavo yavaiva vawana zvichienderana nemurairo waJehovha neruoko rwaMozisi.
\v 10 Zvino vakati vasvika pamiganhu yeJoridhan iri munyika yeKenani, vana vaRubheni nevana vaGadhi nehafu yerudzi rwaManase ndokuvaka aritari paJoridhani, aritari huru pakuona.
\p
\v 11 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakanzwa kuchinzi: Tarirai, vana vaRubheni nevana vaGadhi nehafu yerudzi rwaManase vavaka aritari pakaritarisana neKenani, pamiganhu yeJoridhani, kurutivi rwevana vaIsraeri.
\p
\v 12 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakati vachinzwa, ungano yese yevana vaIsraeri yakaunganira paShiro kukwira kwavari kuhondo.
\v 13 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakatuma kuvna vaRubheni uye kuvana vaGadhi uye kuhafu yerudzi rwaManase panyika yeGiriyadhi Pinehasi mwanakomana waEriazari mupristi,
\v 14 nemachinda gumi naye, muchinda umwe paimba imwe neimwe yemadzibaba kubva pamarudzi ese eVaIsraeri; umwe neumwe wavo ari musoro weimba yemadzibaba avo pazvuru zveVaIsraeri.
\p
\v 15 Ivo vakasvika kuvana vaRubheni nekuvana vaGadhi nekuhafu yerudzi rwaManase kunyika yeGiriyadhi ndokutaura navo vachiti:
\v 16 Ndizvo zvinoreva ungano yaJehovha: Chii kudarika uku kwamakadarikira Mwari waIsraeri, muchitsauka nhasi pakutevera Jehovha, pakuzvivakira aritari, kuti mupandukire Jehovha nhasi?
\v 17 Ko kuipa kwaPeori kudukusa kwatiri here, kwatisati tacheneswa kwachiri nanhasi kunyange pakava nedambudziko pakati peungano yaJehovha,
\v 18 kuti imwi mutsauke nhasi pakutevera Jehovha? Zvino kuchati kana imwi muchimupandukira nhasi, mangwana achatsamwira ungano yese yaIsraeri.
\v 19 Asi zvirokwazvo kana nyika yenyu yenhaka yenyu isina kuchena, yambukirai kunyika yenhaka yaJehovha, pagere tabhenakeri yaJehovha, muzviwanire nhaka pakati pedu; asi musapandukira Jehovha kana kutipandukira pakuzvivakira aritari kunze kwearitari yaJehovha Mwari wedu.
\v 20 Akani mwanakomana waZera haana kudarika here nekudarika pachinhu chakayereswa, kutsamwa ndokuwira ungano yese yaIsraeri? Uye murume uyu haana kufa ari ega pakudarika kwake.
\p
\v 21 Ipapo vana vaRubheni nevana vaGadhi nehafu yerudzi rwaManase vakapindura ndokuti kumisoro yezvuru vaVaIsraeri:
\v 22 Mwari, wevamwari, iye Jehovha Mwari wevamwari, Jehovha ndiye anoziva, naIsraeri ngaazive, kana kwaiva pakupanduka kana nekutsauka kuna Jehovha, musatiponesa nhasi,
\v 23 kuti takazvivakira aritari, kutsauka pakutevera Jehovha; kana kuti takapa pamusoro payo chipo chinopiswa kana chipo chechidyiwa, kana kuita pamusoro payo chipo chekuyananisa, Jehovha amene ngaatsvake.
\v 24 Asi kana tisina kuita chinhu ichi nekuchenjera uye nekufunga, tichiti: Mangwana vana venyu vachataura nevana vedu vachiti: Imwi munei naJehovha Mwari waIsraeri?
\v 25 Nokuti Jehovha wakaita Joridhani muganhu pakati pedu nemwi, imwi vana vaRubheni nevana vaGadhi; hamuna mugove kuna Jehovha; saizvozvo vana venyu vangaregesa vana vedu kutya Jehovha.
\v 26 Saka takati: Ngatizvigadzire ikozvino kuvaka aritari, isiri yezvipiriso zvinopiswa, kana yekubayira;
\v 27 asi chive chapupu pakati pedu nemwi nemazera edu shure kwedu kuti tishumire shumiro yahovha pamberi pake nezvipiriso zvedu zvinopiswa, nezvibairo zvedu, nezvipiriso zvedu zvokuyananisa, kuti vana venyu varege kuzoti kuvana vedu panguva inouya, Hamuna mugove kuna Jehovha.
\v 28 Naizvozvo takati: Kana vachizodaro kwatiri kana kuvana vedu panguva inouya, isu tichati: Tarirai muone mufananidzo weatari yaJehovha, yakaitwa namadzibaba edu, isati iri yezvipiriso zvinopiswa, kana yokubayirapo; asi chapupu pakati pedu nemi.
\v 29 Mwari atibatsire, tirege kumukira Jehovha, nokutsauka nhasi pakutevera Jehovha, tichavaka atari yezvipiriso zvinopiswa neyezvipiriso zvoupfu, kana yokubayirapo, parutivi rweatari yaJehovha, Mwari wedu, iri pamberi petabhenakeri yake.
\p
\v 30 Zvino Pinehasi mupristi, namachinda eungano, ivo vakuru vezvuru zvaVaIsraeri, vakange vanaye, vakati vanzwa mashoko akataurwa navana vaRubheni, navana vaGadhi, navana vaManase, vakafara nazvo.
\v 31 Pinehasi, mwanakomana waEriazari mupristi, akati kuvana vaRubheni, nokuvana vaGadhi, nokuvana vaManase: Nhasi tinoziva kuti Jehovha ari pakati pedu, nokuti hamuna kudarikira Jehovha pachinhu ichi; makarwira vana vaIsraeri zvino paruoko rwaJehovha.
\p
\v 32 Ipapo Pinehasi, mwanakomana waEriazari mupristi, namachinda vakabva kuvana vaRubheni navana vaGadhi, panyika yeGiriyadhi, vakadzokera kunyika yeKenani, kuvana vaIsraeri, vakavadzosera shoko iro.
\v 33 Zvino shoko iro rakafadza vana vaIsraeri, vana vaIsraeri vakakudza Mwari; havana kuzotaura kuti vachanorwa navo, kuti vaparadze nyika makange mugere vana vaRubheni navana vaGadhi.
\v 34 Zvino vana vaRubheni navana vaGadhi vakatumidza atari iyo: Ndicho chapupu pakati pedu, kuti Jehovha ndiye Mwari.
